{"tid":1689622,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人講？11.2政府武力鎮壓民主派選舉集會","createTime":"2019-11-03T02:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T04:45:40.000Z","uid":276716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7b0543c3a16e03af71a77749f4b63fc1153616","tid":1689622,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"警暴已經人所共知，但好多人，尤其外國政界，未清楚香港嘅選舉情況。<br />\n<br />\n11.2要吸引到國際關注，就一定要將重點放喺<span style=\"color: red;\">政府鎮壓民主派選舉聚會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n1. 聚會未開始，政府恫嚇候選人會發射催淚彈<br />\n2. 軍警舉槍鎮壓集會選民<br />\n3. 民主派候選人被拘捕<br />\n<br />\n上面幾點，配合DQ Gphone，足以令政府以後所有選舉嘅公信力降到零，國際上會視之為俄羅斯、古巴、委內瑞拉同一類，由獨裁者操控嘅選舉。"},{"pid":"8025c8ff08eee20c6ae932a1a920116212f1d857","tid":1689622,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:17:22.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"1a9dff77f378052744bfb108e18695f8d66840fa","tid":1689622,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c0cf75285c85c710409ff1323572b8ee1346e88","tid":1689622,"uid":266536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"推 維園現場超和平 結果黑警突襲"},{"pid":"377f4d76da8edd4a9ab14f2caedca42cc8b556e2","tid":1689622,"uid":103353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5f0d86c31ac9cbb7362a44b0eab0a984fa07d89","tid":1689622,"uid":4798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:45:40.000Z","msg":"國際戰線呀喂"}]}